graph TD;
    image[image</br>32*208*208*3]         --> conv1[convolutional</br>3*3*3*16];

    conv2[convolutional</br>3*3*16*16]    -->|relu| pool2[max pooling</br>3*3,1*1];

    fcon2[fully connected</br>128*128]    -->|relu| fcon3[fully connected</br>128*2];
